the United States gain a knowl-
edge of geography, foreign lan-
guages and cultures of other
nations.

A major reason why the
United States. has not had a
huge amount of success in the
Japanese markets is our igno-
rance of and arrogance toward
the Japanese people and cul-
ture.

Multiculturalism, from my
